{"tid":1651222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部駐港公署譴責克魯茲喪失道德良知","createTime":"2019-10-13T09:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T11:00:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48f02aec01d0fc004b2f2e874b831529775ddef3","tid":1651222,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"外交部駐港公署譴責，美國參議員克魯茲在港期間，聲稱沒有見到黑衣暴徒，不斷訴諸極端暴力的行為，卻厚顏無恥污蔑極度克制的香港警隊為&ldquo;暴力鎮壓&rdquo;，已到令人不齒的地步，喪失起碼的是非標準和道德良知，他為極端暴力分子搖旗吶喊、撐腰打氣，對香港事務和中國內政指手畫腳，公署表示極度憤慨。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示， 正是各種外國干預勢力及黑手，充當香港極端暴力分子的代言人和保護傘，與香港禍國亂港分子相互勾結，暴徒才會有恃無恐、無法無天，香港局勢才會惡化到今天這樣令人痛心的地步，強調中方捍衛國家主權安全與香港繁榮穩定的決心堅定不移，警告克魯茲之流不得在中國土地撒野。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1186599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1186599&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=f55abd77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1186599</a>"},{"pid":"2a5ddf0d094d7392886346533a848939977d77bc","tid":1651222,"uid":191762,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那仲有一兩年收皮有得講就好講"},{"pid":"3c4f775a3397d77ef28fe0cd4af4ae655ff7b07e","tid":1651222,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:30:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"242c112dc36af99eeb704858fce1403f2a5032e6","tid":1651222,"uid":70745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:31:40.000Z","msg":"又助攻，貿易戰傾掂數未？"},{"pid":"b35942a52dfe2e082676f085082ac9131f12572d","tid":1651222,"uid":71428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"242c112dc36af99eeb704858fce1403f2a5032e6","tid":1651222,"uid":70745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:31:40.000Z","msg":"又助攻，貿易戰傾掂數未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:53:22.